This is a bloodbath. Canva, Adobe, Looka, Logo.com, Design.com, Wix, Recraft, LogoAI \'97 all the heavyweights. Do NOT try to compete on this keyword directly.\

\f0\b The long-tail vertical opportunity \'97 this is where it gets interesting:
\f1\b0 \
When I searched "brand kit for restaurants AI" and "brand kit for real estate agents AI" \'97 
\f0\b there are NO dedicated programmatic SEO pages targeting these verticals.
\f1\b0  Results are generic "AI tools for [industry]" listicles, Amazon Kindle books, and industry-specific content tools (menu makers, listing flyers). Nobody has built the 
